Polar Capital LLP Key Developments

Polar Capital Announces Management Changes
Jul 20 17
Polar Capital announced that Gavin Rochussen has joined Polar Capital as CEO. He succeeds Tim Woolley, who has moved to a non-executive position. Rochussen was previously group CEO at JO Hambro Capital Management. Between 2003 and 2008 he was CEO of wealth management firm Fleming Family & Partners.


