 Career History



Portfolio Manager

                                    Current                


Polar Capital LLP


                  Polar Capital is a specialist, research-driven manager which performs rigorous fundamental analysis, aiming to provide differentiated risk-adjusted returns over the long term through their long-only and alternative  funds which are diversified by asset class, geography and sector.The firm selects stocks based on their potential for returns and focuses on management quality, new growth markets, the globalization of major technology trends, exploiting international valuation anomalies and sector volatility.                




Portfolio Manager

                                    2009 - 2010                


AXA Investment Managers (UK) Ltd.


                  AXA IM-UK is an active, multi-specialist manager which has expertise in global fixed-income, pan-European and global equities, structured products, private equity, real estate and multi-management.The firm focuses on investment areas where they have a competitive edge within each asset class.  They are organized in small investment teams dedicated to a specific instrument, sector, region or strategy. Each team is supported by a shared pool of fundamental research resources and empowered to make investment decisions.AXA IM-UK's research is organized along investment strategy, equity and fixed-income and is supported by proprietary quantitative resources and an extensive company visit program.                





 Other Affiliations




              Ming Xian Kemp is affiliated with
                            Polar Capital LLP, AXA Investment Managers (UK) Ltd..
            





