Polar Capital LLP | EQ Investors


































































HomeInvesting with EQFund GroupsPolar Capital LLP








 
Polar Capital LLP

Polar Capital is a specialist investment management company founded in 2001. Since then, it has steadily grown and currently supports 12 investment teams managing 24 funds and five managed accounts across a range of long-only and alternative products, with combined AUM of £8.4 billion (as of 31/12/2016).






Manages these EQ rated funds


